title: Roald Dahl - The Vicar of Nibbleswicke & Other Stories
description:
The Vicar of Nibbleswicke & Other Stories 

Written by Roald Dahl 

Read by Stephen Fry 


Released by Random House AudioBooks in 1992

Length: 2 hours, 59 minutes


The stories on this recording include pieces from the 1950s and 1960s to "The Vicar of Nibbleswicke" which was completed just before Roald Dahl died.


Contents:

The Vicar of Nibbleswicke
Taste
Edward the Conqueror
Mr Botibol
The Hitchhiker
The Landlady



File format:  mp3  (64 Kbps, 24 KHz, 2 Channels, Joint Stereo)
